code: @Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     out.writeString(name).     out.writeBoolean(available).     out.writeBoolean(enabled). }

@Override public final XContentBuilder toXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     builder.startObject().     innerXContent(builder, params).     return builder.endObject(). }
protected void innerXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     builder.field(AVAILABLE_XFIELD, available).     builder.field(ENABLED_XFIELD, enabled). }
